{# Template: self-critique-revision/self-critique-convergence-check.j2 #}
{# goal: Compute normalized convergence metric for self-critique/revision cycles. #}

[inference]
temperature = 0.1
reasoning_effort = "medium"
verbosity = "terse"
max_tokens = 1000
thinking_budget = "standard"

Compute convergence where 0 means major critique issues are resolved and incremental quality gains are sufficiently small.

Input:
```json
{
  "critique_result": {{ critique_result | tojson }},
  "revision_result": {{ revision_result | tojson }}
}
```

Return JSON only:
```json
{
  "convergence_metric": 0.0,
  "rationale": "short explanation",
  "blockers": []
}
```
